summary: An ordinance authorizing and directing the City Treasurer to cancel the unpaid assessment levied for the improvement of Murray Avenue et al, by trunk sewer, Local Improvement District No. 3402, on portions of the south half of the southeast quarter of the northeast quarter of the southeast quarter of Section 23, Township 24 North, Range 3 East, W.M., which have been deeded to the City of Seattle for street purposes.
